  -i, --ignore-rules <IGNORE_RULES>    Names of rules to exclude, separated by a comma (no spaces). [default: ]
  -w, --with-timing                    Show the time taken by the function.
  -m, --min-r-version <MIN_R_VERSION>  The mimimum R version to be used by the linter. Some rules only work starting from a specific version.
      --output-format <OUTPUT_FORMAT>  Output serialization format for violations. [default: concise] [possible values: concise, json]
